CatDescriptText: A mural on the wall in the background of the church reads as follows, "Therefore whosoever heareth these sayings of mine and doeth them I will liken him unto a wise man which built his house upon a rock and the rain descended and the floods came and the winds blew and beat upon the house; and it fell not because it was founded upon a rock."
TitMainTitle: Group of well dressed men and women seated on pews, with man at organ in foreground and men and women in background
